notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: J.C. and B.Z. contributed to the conception and design of the study and data analysis; W.D., K.L., J.S., and J.C. collected the plant material and performed distillation and GC-MS analysis; K.L. and S.C. carried out bioactivity test; W.D. and J.C. wrote the manuscript. All authors have read and agreed to the published version of the manuscript.
